description.content:
Expert Python Django Developer for Custom Web Application Development


Need a skilled developer to bring your web app idea to life? With 5+ years of experience in Python, Django, and web development, I create high-performance solutions tailored to your needs.


Technologies I Use:

  • Frontend: HTML, CSS, Bootstrap, JavaScript, jQuery, Ajax, React
  • Backend: Python, Django, Django Rest Framework, Custom Python Scripts
  • Automation: Selenium for testing, Unit testing, Service testing
  • DevOps: Docker, Jenkins, AWS
  • Databases: MySQL, PostgreSQL, SQLite, DynamoDB
  • Other Tools: Git, Redis, Celery, Nginx, DigitalOceanm, Apollo, graphQL, Prisma


Services I Offer:

  • Custom web development using Python/Django
  • REST API creation & integration
  • Docker for smooth deployment
  • Selenium for automated testing
  • Unit testing, Service testing
  • Data integration
  • Responsive web design
  • Database management 
  • Deployment & support


Why Choose Me?

  • Customer Satisfaction Your needs come first
  • Custom Solutions Tailored to you
  • Full Support From start to finish
  • On-Time Delivery Every project, every time 
  • Affordable Rates Quality at a great price


Lets create your Web Application ! Contact me today.

questionsAndAnswers.question: What services do you offer as a Python Django developer
questionsAndAnswers.answer: I specialize in custom web development, REST API creation, Docker deployment, Selenium-based testing, API integration, responsive web design, database management, and more.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you provide support after project delivery?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes! I offer ongoing support to ensure everything runs smoothly after deployment, along with updates and maintenance if needed.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Can you handle both frontend and backend development?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Absolutely! I am proficient in frontend technologies like HTML, CSS, Bootstrap, and JavaScript, as well as backend development using Python, Django, and REST APIs.

questionsAndAnswers.question: How do you ensure the quality of the web applications?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: I use automated testing tools like Selenium, as well as unit and service testing, to ensure your application is robust, error-free, and performs efficiently.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Can you help with API integration?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes! I have experience integrating services and APIs into Django applications, ensuring seamless data flow and functionality.

questionsAndAnswers.question: What is your usual project turnaround time?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Turnaround time depends on the project’s complexity, but I always prioritize delivering projects on time, without compromising quality.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you offer containerized deployment using Docker?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, I use Docker for containerization to ensure your application can be easily deployed, scaled, and maintained across different environments.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Can you work with cloud services like AWS?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, I have experience working with AWS for hosting, database management, and setting up cloud-based services.
